              %strong BruCON 0x0B
            (2019)
            &mdash; (only assisted with creating UI for a vulnerable website)
          %li.link
            %a{ href: "https://nonamecon.org", target: '_blank', rel: 'noopener noreferrer' }<
              %strong NoNameCon
            (2018) &mdash; Practical Cybersecurity Conference (created admin interface, was one of the Game Masters)
          %li.link
            %a{ href: "https://uisgcon.org/en/about-uisgcon", target: '_blank', rel: 'noopener noreferrer' }<
              %strong UISGCon
            \#10, #11, #12 (2014-2016) &mdash; Ukrainian InfoSec conference held by Non Government Organisation
            %strong «Ukrainian Information Security Group»
          %li.link
            The Cybersecurity Olympiad
            %strong «HackIT-2015»
